name: VC3 (Part of Rebellion)
description:
VC3 is a split off group from the German r/placede discord server, which was banned due to opposing the strict moderation of r/placede.
The name is representing the voice channel "VC3", in which the split off started by the channel getting deleted from the r/placede discord, due to the group criticizing the administration and moderation. The group merged with the already existing group Rebellion
